#### qmd -> rmd（见脚注）

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
format: 
  pdf:
    template: cumcm.tex
# 修改为
output:
  bookdown::pdf_document2: 
    template: cumcm.tex
    latex_engine: xelatex
```
:::
